PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1992-2560, which authorized for the borrowing by way of loan or by the issue and sale of Treasury bills or Treasury notes in the January 1, 1993 to March 31, 1993 period, subject to the just-passed Borrowing Authority Act, 1992-93 (No. 2).
